      "content": "it does feel like surrendering is the only way to actually find some peace. if the struggle is just a futile cycle, then maybe there's more dignity in just opting out rather than forcing ourselves to keep playing a game that was rigged from the start. don't you think there's a certain kind of honesty in just letting go?",
